> **A high-performance backend for decentralized betting on Solana blockchain**

## ✨ FEATURES ✨

### 🏗️ DECENTRALIZED ARCHITECTURE
![Blockchain](https://img.shields.io/badge/Blockchain-Transparent-blue)
- Immutable betting transactions on Solana
- Smart contract-based logic
- Transparent and verifiable results

### 👥 USER MANAGEMENT
![Authentication](https://img.shields.io/badge/Auth-Wallet_Integrated-blue)
- Secure wallet authentication
- Non-custodial user accounts
- Role-based access control

### 💰 BET PROCESSING
![Betting](https://img.shields.io/badge/Bets-Secure-green)
- End-to-end bet lifecycle management
- Real-time validation
- Automated settlement

### ⛓️ BLOCKCHAIN INTERACTION
![Solana](https://img.shields.io/badge/Solana-RPC_Integrated-purple)
- Seamless transaction execution
- On-chain data retrieval
- Event listening

### ⏰ CRON JOB FUNCTIONALITY
![Automation](https://img.shields.io/badge/Automated-Scheduled-orange)
```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Start] --> B[Check Pending Bets]
    B --> C{Time Expired?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Process Settlement]
    C -->|No| B
    D --> E[Distribute Winnings]
    E --> F[Update Blockchain]
